1043
01:28:22,487 --> 01:28:23,755
My name is Oh Mi-yeon.

1044
01:28:24,589 --> 01:28:25,824
My daughter is Kang Ji-eun.

1045
01:28:26,357 --> 01:28:29,194
Born June 24, 1999.

1046
01:28:33,298 --> 01:28:34,165
Yeah.

1047
01:28:34,599 --> 01:28:36,618
She's not here.

1048
01:28:36,701 --> 01:28:38,770
It doesn't seem like
she walked this way.

1049
01:28:40,505 --> 01:28:41,890
Did she go to Ji-eun's hospital?

1050
01:28:41,973 --> 01:28:43,525
How could she just
go to the hospital

1051
01:28:43,608 --> 01:28:45,627
without knowing which one it is?

1052
01:28:45,710 --> 01:28:47,679
Ah... right..

1053
01:28:48,646 --> 01:28:49,948
Did she head to the main road?

1054
01:28:52,717 --> 01:28:53,818
I'll go check.

