My name is Oh Mi-yeon.

1065
01:30:18,903 --> 01:30:19,804
Isn't that Ms. Oh over there?

1066
01:30:21,105 --> 01:30:21,973
Pull over.

1067
01:30:22,440 --> 01:30:23,859
Grab the umbrella.

1068
01:30:23,942 --> 01:30:24,809
Yeah.

1069
01:30:30,415 --> 01:30:32,467
Ms. Oh!

1070
01:30:32,550 --> 01:30:35,804
How can you just leave
without saying anything!

1071
01:30:35,887 --> 01:30:37,322
Oh... you're all wet.

1072
01:30:38,790 --> 01:30:39,975
Are you bleeding?

1073
01:30:40,058 --> 01:30:41,042
Get in the car, okay?

1074
01:30:41,125 --> 01:30:42,077
Get in. Hurry.

1075
01:30:42,160 --> 01:30:45,163
Ji-eun. I need to
get to Ji-eun. Quickly.

